<headline>Special Weather Statement issued January 14 at 8:44AM MST  by NWS GreatFalls</headline>
<description>...Patchy Fog in and Near the Milk River Valley This Morning...
Patchy fog reducing visibility to one-half mile or less has
developed in and near the Milk River Valley this morning. This fog
will likely be slow to diminish today, lasting into at least the
early afternoon. If you encounter fog, slow down and leave room
between you and the vehicle in front of you.</description>
